project.objective: The Dutch Ministry of Health, Welfare and Sport will organize an international conference focusing on the implementation eHealth in health systems and the use by citizens. This conference will be organized in joint cooperation with the European Commission and aligned with the European conference of the Healthcare Information and Management Systems Society, and together is called the 'eHealth Week 2016'. It is scheduled 6-10 of June 2016 in Amsterdam, The Netherlands.
project.title: eHealth Week 2016
